snippet.title: The Sims 4: Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Create your own weirder stories in The Sims 4 on September 2nd, 2014.

Get it now: http://bit.ly/1BLMF1d

Control the mind, body, and heart of your Sims in The Sims 4. The Sims you create are full of life, defined by their unique personalities and new emotions.
